    "headline": "Pentair Announces Quarterly Cash Dividend of $0.27",
    "summary": "LONDON, May 04, 2026--Pentair plc (NYSE: PNR) announced today that it will pay a regular quarterly cash dividend of $0.27 per share on August 7, 2026 to shareholders of record at the close of business on July 24, 2026. This is the 50th consecutive year that Pentair has increased its dividend.",
